# check_irida_sequencing_run_upload_status
# check the upload status of a sequencing run
# lightweight wrapper - no WARNING, no countdown
#
# NOTE: this function is essentially a duplicate of get_irida_sequence_run with a single ID.
#       it is included here for scripting clarity and completeness.
#
# example:
#   check_irida_sequencing_run_upload_status 801
#   check_irida_sequencing_run_upload_status 801:SequencingRun_2026-04-06
#
# NOTE: non-admin users will only see sequencing runs they created.
#       admin users see all runs. Use get_irida_token_admin to see all runs.
#
# Copyright (C) 2026 George Marselis <george.marselis@vetinst.no>
